│ ScalarEvolution available through R to compute distances relative to the      │
│ first store.\n\nEdit (replace the block between computing Cost and the call   │
│ to R.vectorizeTree):\n- After computing Cost and deciding to vectorize,       │
│ insert a loop over the selected store chain to ensure all pointer operands    │
