│ -------------------- BEGIN --------------------                               │
│ 1. Understanding the Issue:                                                   │
│ The SLP vectorizer is turning four scalar stores at offsets 0, 8, 4294967312, │
│ and 4294967320 into a single <4 x i64> vector store to the base pointer. This │
│ is incorrect because the pointers are not a single contiguous block: two are  │
